WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.671
Hello, young word explorer.

2
00:00:01.671 --> 00:00:04.596
Welcome to Unit 6, All About Bugs.

3
00:00:04.596 --> 00:00:08.774
This unit has 24 vocabulary cards in 4 learning groups.

4
00:00:08.774 --> 00:00:11.699
Group 1 is Bugs and Garden Animals.

5
00:00:11.699 --> 00:00:16.295
Listen for words such as butterfly, cricket, ant, bee, spider, worm.

6
00:00:16.295 --> 00:00:19.220
Group 2 is What Makes an Insect.

7
00:00:19.220 --> 00:00:23.816
Listen for words such as insect, legs, wings, antennae, anthill, web.

8
00:00:23.816 --> 00:00:25.905
Group 3 is Position Words.

9
00:00:25.905 --> 00:00:31.336
Listen for words such as on, under, in, between, above, in front of.

10
00:00:31.336 --> 00:00:34.679
Group 4 is What Bugs Do (Action Words).

11
00:00:34.679 --> 00:00:39.275
Listen for words such as fly, jump, crawl, spin, chirp, collect.

12
00:00:39.275 --> 00:00:49.720
For each word, listen and repeat, read five sentences, notice the word type, practise spelling, write your own sentence, and ask the tutor for help.

13
00:00:49.720 --> 00:00:52.645
You are ready to begin Unit 6.
